{"type": "article", "id": 16157, "title": "August Access system", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-16T06:50:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135558C1RtbZVAknpexPv7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套可以用手机控制门锁的家用系统，包括一个锁，按键盘，内设相机的门铃和配合这个系统的手机 app。使用者可以通过手机控制门锁，即便是不在家的时候，也可以开门放受信任的人进屋，并检查门是否锁上。对于家里有狗或者安排清洁人员进屋是非常方便的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143515B3nDEMT0gj6yLX7K.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614351618dfyCaeB2QTgjlR.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143517YCjsDxIomGah9JOf.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143517IS2vxt6ErjoCmyB7.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"761\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}